title: NY Rep. Reed, PA Sen. Casey, Stimulus Deal
itunes:title: NY Rep. Reed, PA Sen. Casey, Stimulus Deal
description:
Guests: Steven Dennis, Bloomberg Congress reporter, Thomas Hogan, Senior Fellow at the American Institute for Economic Research, Kristen Hawn, Democratic Strategist, and Partner at Rokk Solutions, Eli Yokley, Senior politics reporter at Morning Consult, Rep. Tom Reed, a New York Republican and co-chair of the Problem Solvers Caucus, and Senator Bob Casey, a Pennsylvania Democrat.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
